lead_paragraph: Vincent Janssen is disappointed with AZ Alkmaar after his club rejected a bid from Tottenham Hotspur for the Netherlands international despite the striker insisting on a move.

headline.print_headline: Janssen Frustrated by AZ's Refusal of Spurs Bid
